//Transpiling allows you to generate ECMAScript
This means that you can write code that is compatible with old browsers, while still using the newest tools

//TS supports JS libraries and API documentation
Including Jquery, React, and more you can use tools you're already used to

//TS introduces static typing
Helps structure your code and improve OOP techniques. 
It also makes the code easier to reactor since you can navigate to refrences of function members

//TS uses NPM
Gives access to millions of libraries
